The paper discusses the popularity of online videos and proposes a visualization system to explain and predict their virality. This falls under the category of social media analysis and information retrieval, which is covered by cs.SI and cs.IR. The use of metadata and popularity series of videos suggests the involvement of multimedia analysis (cs.MM) and machine learning (cs.LG). Finally, the system is designed to be accessible to regular users, indicating a focus on human-computer interaction (cs.HC).
